{"type": "article", "id": 42471, "title": "这个波西米亚风的公寓，细节多到你会对着一张图看很久", "description": "说到波西米亚风格，可不只是简单地把层层叠叠的色彩、装饰堆砌在一起，用得不好，整个家就像是打翻了的调色盘，凌乱不堪；用得好，就成了带着自由不羁、热情奔放情绪的另类高级感。", "date": "2017-06-30T23:19:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 14006, "name": "住宅设计"}, {"id": 41866, "name": "波西米亚风格"}, {"id": 41867, "name": "RSRG Arquitetos"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 355, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170628131438fVEBlSpbJXtR67K0.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>设计师的家有多特别？来看看巴西珠宝设计师 Brenda Vidal 的公寓。</p><p>近几年你可能见过了太多北欧风、日式风、美式风的房子，但 Brenda Vidal 这间公寓玩的波西米亚风格，倒是罕见，她的家是用很多色彩、纹理、图案和各种风格的装饰品混搭出来的，透着满满的艺术感，又不缺生活烟火气。</p><p>公寓位于圣保罗的 Ibiapinopolis 街，接手这间老宅改造任务的，是纽约时尚设计师 <a href=\"http://www.anastrumpf.com.br/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ana Strumpf</a> 和圣保罗工作室 <a href=\"https://www.rsrg.com.br/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RSRG Arquitetos</a>。</p><p>说到波西米亚风格，可不只是简单地把层层叠叠的色彩、装饰堆砌在一起，用得不好，整个家就像是打翻了的调色盘，凌乱不堪；用得好，就成了带着自由不羁、热情奔放情绪的另类高级感。</p><p>乍一看，Brenda Vidal 的公寓像个小型家居装饰博物馆，细细看过去，称得上是一场视觉盛宴。</p><p>公寓的每个房间都有一个主题色彩，比如粉色、橘色，薄荷绿色以及天蓝色，但做法并不常见，不是刷个单色墙壁，再搭配一些同色系的地板、饰品或是窗帘那么简单，相反，设计师用了很多或与主题色调呼应或是与其形成对比的色彩，这种关联或对抗的节奏在一个空间反而能够创造出一种和谐的效果。</p><p>拿 Brenda Vidal 的家庭工作室来说，薄荷绿是那个主角，除了一面薄荷绿单色墙壁，另有一面贴着海泡石绿色花卉图案壁纸的墙，烘托出整个空间的清爽和活力，白色的搁架单元和复古质感的书桌上摆放着书籍、记事本、草绘板、马克笔，面料样品以及一些灵感小物等等，看似凌乱地堆砌在桌前或是搁架上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131628w50UlCVu3BTkzaqt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.492969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">白色搁架单元</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131629XZWO5o0hIupTFLCS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666797\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">工作室全貌</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131629p5JOd61GsMnjtBFE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">木质移动茶台</figcaption></figure></div><p>当然，创作者也需要在紧张忙碌的工作中偷个闲。在工作室里，Brenda Vidal 还给自己置办了一个复古质感的木质移动茶台，上下两层分置着咖啡机、茶叶罐、水杯、茶杯、咖啡杯等等。一把黑色钢制线条的休闲椅，上面搭着一个蝴蝶图案的白色软垫。窗边另有一个摆放着鲜花的圆桌搭配着三把座椅，自成一处小型会客区。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131711gR0PGhKWkI4tBLCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">工作室小型会客区</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706281317119DECBoArO83w5GWa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">休闲椅</figcaption></figure></div><p>墙壁上挂满了包括植物、动物以及建筑等不同主题的水彩画，地板上也散落着装饰画和艺术设计类书籍，便于主人随时拿取，查阅资料，汲取灵感。</p><p>为客厅定下基调的，是一整面挂满装饰艺术画的粉色墙壁。黑色皮质茶几、白色棉布沙发、棕褐色皮革扶手椅以及白色长绒地毯围出一块舒适的客厅中心区域，色彩明丽的鲜花、装饰画和沙发靠垫调节着整个空间的情绪。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706281318477nDNuYViX4rzPITq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">客厅粉色主题装饰墙</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131847oR1p3vsmbFuwzCcq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">小酒桌</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131849VaT3b0ve9EYiu7Fj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">客厅全貌</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131849ipCxPL41REGYl5FA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">白色窗帘上挂着水彩装饰画</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131848lSsWqxLphEZ0IrBg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131850pcChIduJb8rFzVNL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666797\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">客厅中心区域</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131851jgt6WckiKdxpfZ3X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628131851UHYA5bmsn2ZI1V04.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017062813185164zHWNM0DBCZFr9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666797\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">客厅一侧的用餐区</figcaption></figure></div><p>三个卧室也以不同的色彩区隔开来，儿童的房间刷成了半高的橘色墙壁，主卧用上了安静沉稳的蓝色，另有一间次卧做成了白色系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132155OHZsiLm8gYnBwQ3C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132156uqC8xnIWFP1Xt0E9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132157vcBnOzHFV0baLey4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132157cugkj7p0EatsmZFD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在儿童卧房，从壁纸、床品到地毯，花卉、蝴蝶及小鸟图案被大面积运用，搁板上堆满了大大小小的毛绒玩具，试图营造出小女生对于童话世界的美妙幻想，草绿色、浅粉色以及薄荷绿色的斗柜、桌椅，也使得整个空间的色彩更加丰富。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132217HRqgbNlw5JMh7yU6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132217MQPYlVdZuiXvA9mr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706281322180NFWhkeZ62RbKfnx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132219ToI0hZ3AlbUDzi9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132219dIqXxHTtChKbf6MU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>主卧在用色上要克制很多，清清爽爽的蓝色是主人为逃脱城市喧嚣生活的一种选择，从床架到床品的选择也都呼应了主色调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132242ZCqMDwhzaGtAo215.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132242MLK1HScPAdQC6zqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170628132242vmUADRpFKTOcrNMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.yatzer.com/ana-strumpf-rsrg-arquitetos-apartment-ibiapinopolis\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yatzer</a></p>"}